Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:27.08,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}que nossa compatibilidade
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:30.33,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5} não é lá essas coisas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:33.87,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}ele seria um impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:37.38,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Não, não pode, não se deixe enganar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:41.34,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Quem decide o destino sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:43.17,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Isso mesmo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:48.14,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}este é o amor verdadeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:53.98,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}É o tipo de coisa que, após morrermos
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:58.36,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}será exibida em um museu de arte.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:04.82,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por isso, me deixe sempre em primeiro lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:08.41,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Me ame com todo carinho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:14.54,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}até que estas mãos que seguramos se fundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:18.42,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Vamos ficar sempre nessa vibe boa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:21.84,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Se formos nós dois, será moleza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:28.05,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Fique ao meu lado, mesmo que estejamos "chapados" de amor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:30.89,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por favor.
